snippet.title: Quake - The Seal Of Nehahra (Opening Movie)
snippet.description:
This is the 4 hour opening movie to the Quake mod Nehahra. I trimmed it so the loading screens were cropped out. I used the 
Quake sourceport "Darkplaces"
https://icculus.org/twilight/darkplaces/download.html

Quake Game
http://store.steampowered.com/app/2310/

Seal Of Nehahra mod.
http://www.moddb.com/mods/nehahra/downloads/nehahra-full
